          <td width=395> 
            <p class=body2>With offshore sports gaming now 
              a multi-billion dollar industry, it can be difficult for the consumer 
              to separate the reputable sports book from the less so, the exceptional 
              from the merely average. My staff and I, with the help of other 
              industry pros, have investigated many of the present offshore operations. 
              Those that met or surpassed our standards for 2001 are included 
              in this report.<br>
              </p>
            <p class=body2>Our analysis has shown that these 
              offshore sports books are honorable and financially strong, but 
              we welcome your experiences. Send your comments, positive or negative, 
              to Sheridan Specials, Inc., P.O. Box 2122, Mobile, AL 36652, 1-251-476-1122.</p>
